# Partners managed via Decap CMS
#
# Each *.json file in this folder represents a partner added via the CMS at /admin.
# The CMS auto-creates these — don't edit by hand unless you know what you're doing.
#
# Schema (validated by src/content.config.ts):
#   { id, name, instagram?, sector, logo, description?, reach? }
#
# These merge with the static partners list at src/data/partners.ts via loadAllPartners().
